Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.41,0:01:02.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在播出  水母迷会谈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:02.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now "The Jellyson Group"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:02.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,454)}水母迷会谈
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.75,0:01:07.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚上好  欢迎收看水母迷会谈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:07.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good evening and welcome to "The Jellyson Group,"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.79,0:01:12.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村最强捉水母节目  仅此一家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:12.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom's best and only show about jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.13,0:01:16.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚的嘉宾有水母时尚记者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:13.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My guests tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:16.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are jellyfishing fashion journalist
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.05,0:01:17.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,法布莉卡欧莱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:17.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fabrica Olay
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.47,0:01:21.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知名水母杂技师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:21.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Famed jellyfish juggler
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.01,0:01:22.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小丑老鱼兄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:22.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fish-O The Clown
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.02,0:01:28.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有某个叫海绵宝宝的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:28.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And something called a SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.02,0:01:34.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚谈论的主题是月光水母
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:34.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tonight we will be discussing the moon jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.99,0:01:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每25年一遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only seen once every 25 years
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.32,0:01:42.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,即将迁徙经过裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:42.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will soon be migrating through Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.41,0:01:43.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,容我插一句
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:43.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I can just interrupt
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.83,0:01:47.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没证据能表明这种水母真实存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:47.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there's no evidence this jellyfish even exists
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.08,0:01:49.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁看到了  更何况又有谁捉到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:49.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Has anyone seen it, much less caught it?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海参凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin C. Cucumber
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世上最伟大的水母捕手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the greatest jellyfisher who ever lived
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.38,0:01:55.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉到过月光水母
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:55.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,caught the moon jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放他广为流传的视频  看猎捕全过程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Roll his famous moon catching clip
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.51,0:02:01.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:01.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I caught it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.85,0:02:04.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉到月光水母了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:04.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I caught the moon jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.10,0:02:06.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:06.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.98,0:02:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那视频是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That video is a fake
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it looked real to me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That fish is real--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.27,0:02:13.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是造假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:13.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a fake
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.98,0:02:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耍诈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A ruse
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.57,0:02:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿大鞋的笨小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You big-shoed buffoon
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.32,0:02:16.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,眼不瞎都看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:16.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyone could see it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.24,0:02:17.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明明就有月光水母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:17.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The moon jellyfish is a fact
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.20,0:02:18.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:18.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.24,0:02:19.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母货真价实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:19.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not fake
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.36,0:02:22.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定会捉到月光水母  向你们证明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:22.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll prove it to you by catching the moon jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.53,0:02:23.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟凯文当年一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:23.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just like Kevin did
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:27.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(364,272)}暂停
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先前跟你怎么说的  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did I tell you, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是能找来凯文帮我忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe if I can get Kevin to help me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就能有机会捉到月光水母了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have a chance to catch that moon jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.67,0:02:37.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道要上哪去找凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:37.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I know just where to find Kevin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1084,718)}水母捕手
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.34,0:02:41.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在水母捕手俱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:41.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At the Jellyspotters Clubhouse
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.69,0:02:55.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:55.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.53,0:02:56.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在找
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:56.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.62,0:03:09.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文  真的是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:09.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin, is it really you?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我配不上你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not worthy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  配不上你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Not Worthy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.21,0:03:17.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:17.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你成水母捕手俱乐部部长了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the president of the Jellyspotters Club?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure am
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家抽了签
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We drew straws
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1090,920)}吸管
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.72,0:03:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我第一个把签全吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I was the first one to eat them all
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.47,0:03:26.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:26.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's great
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.76,0:03:28.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海参凯文在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:28.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is Kevin Cucumber here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:32.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(268,990)}吸管
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.27,0:03:32.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说那位书呆海黄瓜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:32.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean the guy that looks like a nerdy pickle?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.40,0:03:36.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,俱乐部好几年前就把他踢出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:36.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He got kicked out of the club years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.23,0:03:38.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早就神隐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:38.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and mysteriously disappeared
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.78,0:03:43.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都不知道他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:43.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one knows where he is
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你想找他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:45.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But if you want to find him
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是他现在的住址
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here's his current address
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.42,0:03:59.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,林中小屋路123号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:59.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,123 Shack in the Woods Lane
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫我部长派大星才对  老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's President Patrick to you, Sonny Jim
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以帮我续杯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I get a refill on these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1232,536)}吸管
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,树林到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, these are the woods
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,眼前也就只有这一条小路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and this is the only lane I see
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:21.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This must be the place
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.95,0:04:28.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:28.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.66,0:04:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.62,0:04:31.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:31.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You here?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.09,0:04:49.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该去遛遛了  金盏花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:49.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for walkies, Miss Marigold
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,阿姨你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在找海参凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for Kevin C. Cucumber
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有看到他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you seen him?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.53,0:05:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.61,0:05:06.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:06.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:07.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.91,0:05:12.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来我林中秘密耻辱洞干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:12.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here at my secret forest shame hole?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在找你啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looking for you, silly
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.70,0:05:17.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要向大师请教秘诀  猎捕月光水母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need some moon jellyfish-catching tips
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the master
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.33,0:05:18.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:18.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,曾经可能拥有过的技能  我全都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've lost any skills I might have once had
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连一般的水母都忘了怎么捉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't remember how to catch a regular jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就连怎么着凉感冒都不会了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't even remember how to catch a cold
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(890,920)}捉
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系  凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, don't worry, Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以帮你东山再起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can get you back in shape
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后一起捉到月光水母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then we can catch the moon jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.23,0:05:42.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就可以重回巅峰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:42.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then you'll be on top again
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟以前一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:44.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like the old days
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.19,0:05:46.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:46.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.49,0:05:50.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,值得一试
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:50.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's worth a try
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.24,0:05:51.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:51.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.49,0:05:54.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我多年以来最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:54.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the best day I've had in years
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是先帮你打理干净好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'll clean you up first
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文回来了  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin is back, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:37.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(450,490)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然帮你打理好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that you're looking the part
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.37,0:06:42.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那现在就来帮你重拾捉水母技能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:40.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's shake the rust
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,off those jellyfishing skills, shall we?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是先从稍微简单点的起步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'll start with something a little easier
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小水母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jelly babies
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  要简单得不止一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, maybe something a lot easier
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去捉吧  凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, go ahead, Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.74,0:07:17.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甩出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:17.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take your--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.79,0:07:18.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最强一网
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:18.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,best swing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又会捉水母了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a jellyfisher again
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:34.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(848,474)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.85,0:07:37.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来动真格了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:37.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, now for the real deal
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.35,0:07:40.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉月光水母的第一步是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:40.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's step one in catching the moon jellyfish?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个我会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know this one
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等待月光降临  水母现形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait for the moon to come out so we can see it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.82,0:07:49.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一步答得好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:49.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good step one
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:52.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it comes
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.38,0:08:10.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文  第二步是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:10.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, Kevin, what's step two?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.72,0:08:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:11.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kevin?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.18,0:08:25.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让水母追我们  用疲劳战术拖累它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:25.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tire the moon jelly out by getting it to chase us
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定就是第二步了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That must be step two, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没有第二步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is no step two
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.32,0:08:33.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我压根不会捉月光水母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:33.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to catch a moon jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.32,0:08:36.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我特地去摄影棚  造假猎捕过程
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:36.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I faked the moon catching on a soundstage
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样大家才会说我酷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so people would think I was cool
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.49,0:08:40.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:40.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你机会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is your chance
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.71,0:08:50.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,趁机捉到它  让你酷回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:50.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to catch it and really be cool
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快躲进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, in here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.47,0:08:58.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好的办法就是包围它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:58.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our best bet is to surround it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你左边包围
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You go left
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.51,0:09:00.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我右边包围
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:00.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll go right
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两面包夹捉到它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll catch it between us
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.18,0:09:05.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,务必记住  关键就在于隐秘行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:05.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And remember, stealth is key
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(844,664)}警察
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱大白天还得上班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some of us work in the morning
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.71,0:09:26.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是月光水母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:26.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the moon jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.34,0:09:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉好像追不到水母  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think we're going to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,catch up to that jellyfish, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.55,0:09:41.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,膝盖都累坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:41.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My knees are getting tired
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.52,0:09:46.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,追不到就设陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:46.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we can't outrun it, maybe we can trap it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是得要来点诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But we'll need some bait
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.77,0:09:50.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,月光水母喜欢吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:50.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What would a moon jellyfish like to eat?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许动  月光水母
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Freeze, moon jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,束手就擒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prepare to be caught
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,月光暗下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're losing the light
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,月光水母快消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The moon jelly's going to disappear
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.97,0:10:24.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,暗下去是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:24.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Losing the light, you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你们就应该需要再来一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe you could use a little
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,月光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,moonlight
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(924,920)}屁股
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  起效了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, it's working
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一点月光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We need more moonlight
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We caught him
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们成功了  凯文
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it, Kevin
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.14,0:11:06.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:06.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没我们这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But there's no we about it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.73,0:11:12.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,月光水母可是我自个儿捉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:12.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the sole catcher of the moon jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.98,0:11:16.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:16.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.03,0:11:17.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:17.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要带我上哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,月光水母要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the moon jelly going?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回家  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Home, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Home
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,25年后它才会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Until it comes back in 25 years, that is
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.51,0:11:47.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:47.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate jellyfishing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:52.06,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}历史笑传
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(702,372)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(718,664)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:57.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:54.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(632,450)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:54.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(770,648)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(726,542)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:57.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(558,546)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.74\pos(656,544)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.20,0:12:05.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  再几步就能看到给你的惊喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:05.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, Sandy, your surprise is just a few more steps away
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  我等不及要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, fellas, I can't wait to--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:13.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1012,528)}裤头村历史博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:13.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1566,894)}礼品店
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村历史博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Museum of Bikini Bottom History
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.87,0:12:16.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们怎么知道要带我来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:16.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How'd y'all know to take me here?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你给我们送了邀请函
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You gave us these invitations
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And boy am I glad I did
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.13,0:12:23.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等不及要来学习
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:23.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just itching to learn
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.68,0:12:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村源远流长的历史了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all about the rich history of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还要记笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:29.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I will be taking notes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.18,0:12:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的研究要刊登在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My research is going to be featured
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.10,0:12:35.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,科研期刊海军报上面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:35.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in a scientific journal, "The Naval Gazette"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1674,492)}海军报
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱盯着肚脐眼看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love gazing at my navel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.44,注释,,0,0,0,,[ gazing（凝视）与 gazette（报纸）谐音\Nnavel（肚脐）与 naval（海军的）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.98,0:12:39.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:39.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那还等什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what are we waiting for?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.49,0:12:46.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请出示门票
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:46.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tickets, please
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.91,0:12:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.66,0:12:54.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:54.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.96,0:12:57.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一张  两张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:57.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One, two--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.25,0:12:59.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘记数到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:59.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,gee, I lost my place
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:05.84,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1226,864)}裤头村\N最老的保安
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  第一样文物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, the first artifact
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.42,0:13:05.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村最老的保安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:05.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom's oldest security guard
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.09,0:13:09.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种老机器人早该清灰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:09.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They should dust these old robots
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.64,0:13:12.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不识字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:12.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:16.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1276,806)}眼观手不动
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.85,0:13:16.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面写眼观手不动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:16.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It says no touching
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  年轻小伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, youngsters
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In you go
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准惹麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, don't cause any trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然就尝尝我的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or you'll have to answer to me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.99,0:13:28.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:28.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.08,0:13:37.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到裤头村创立以前的远古时期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:34.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the ancient past
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:37.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before Bikini Bottom was Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,据大家说这里的展品
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:39.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They say the exhibits here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.04,0:13:42.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最晚可以追溯到万千年前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:42.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,date back at least one gazillion years
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确定有万千那个数吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure about that math?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.42,0:13:47.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家数学可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:47.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They do math good
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:14:02.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1264,248)}裤头峰
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look here, fellas
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,数百万年前  这片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Millions of years ago, this here land
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫做裤头峰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,was called Bikini Top
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.64,0:14:01.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自然侵蚀导致其海拔逐渐下降
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:01.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The elevation was lowered due to natural erosion
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not how it happened
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.74,0:14:09.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来告诉你事实真相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:09.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll tell you the true story
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.03,0:14:09.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:09.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It goes like this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万千年前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:15.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A gazillion years ago
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.16,0:14:18.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个巨型大锚砸中了裤头峰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:18.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Top was hit by a humongous anchor
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.58,0:14:22.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大锚把整座山压平到了海底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The anchor flattened the hill
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the bottom of the ocean
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以裤头村的名字就是这么来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which is why it's called Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(792,920)}底
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.13,0:14:28.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后由于大锚太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:28.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then the anchor was so heavy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.63,0:14:32.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一大堆建筑拔地而起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:30.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that a bunch of buildings
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:32.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,got popped up out of the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:43.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(970,376)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你们是想说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean to tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.20,0:14:54.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在参观的这个大锚博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:54.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the very anchor we're standing inside now
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.95,0:14:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,创造了裤头村吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is the one that created Bikini Bottom?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.00,注释,,0,0,0,,[ bull（胡扯） ]
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来这一层展厅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like this floor
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.88,0:15:13.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,展现出了裤头村的拓荒时代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:13.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,covers Bikini Bottom's old pioneer days
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.06,0:15:17.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是真正的古董石头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:17.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A genuine antique rock
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.64,0:15:20.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拓荒老祖先就用石头骑行了好几里远
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:20.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The pioneers used to ride these babies for miles
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to try
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.52,0:15:24.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:24.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Giddyup
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Calm down
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不准玩套索
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No trick ropin'
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小混混一群
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:46.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn hooligans
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪看好了  拓荒时代里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Sandy, in the old days
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.97,0:15:59.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拓荒老祖先在自家产地给乳海胆挤奶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the pioneers used to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,milk dairy urchins on their homesteads
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那时生活简单又淳朴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was a simple, honest life
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,贪念全无
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without an ounce of greed
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又挤了满满一桶  贝西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another full pail, Bessie
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定可以换不少好货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I reckon I can barter for quite a bit with this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.07,0:16:16.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就换个更厚的手套好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:16.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe for some thicker gloves
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.95,0:16:19.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是拓荒老祖先必须当心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:19.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the pioneers have to watch out
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.41,0:16:22.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肮脏发臭的亡命徒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:22.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for those dirty, stinky outlaws
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,龌龊帮来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:26.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the Grungy Gang
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.46,0:16:28.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪不得哪里味道怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:28.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew something smelled fishy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.76,0:16:35.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要来夺走你家宝贝小海胆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:35.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here to take that valuable little urchin
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快拱手让出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:36.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,off your hands
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.18,0:16:37.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拱蟹爪才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:37.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Claws
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.97,0:16:41.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想得美  肮脏大坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:41.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, you filthy felons
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好海绵警长与海星副手警官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:44.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, Sheriff Pants and Deputy Star
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为这片土地带来了治安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,brought law and order to the land
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要来让你们改邪归正
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here to clean up your act
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.48,0:16:51.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住他们  小的们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:51.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get 'em, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.87,0:17:05.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:05.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubbles
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.96,0:17:09.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,治安变好  商业随之而来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:09.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And with law came commerce
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.04,0:17:13.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是裤头村第一家餐厅开张了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:13.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thus Bikini Bottom's first restaurant was opened
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹奶王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Kreamery
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1188,826)}蟹奶王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(996,794)}纪念奶袋
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.56,0:17:27.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来点纪念奶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:27.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Care for some souvenir milk?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不渴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not thirsty
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.98,0:17:29.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:29.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.65,0:17:31.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要拉倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:31.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Suit yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们一定是踏进了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I reckon we've stepped into
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.83,0:17:43.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村的工业革命时代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:43.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom's Industrial Revolution era
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(888,910)}C{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}型
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,C型船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Model C Boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.25,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 同名原型车为福特制造\N福特发明了第一条汽车制造流水线 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面写着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Says here--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.25,0:17:51.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别念了  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:51.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't read that, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.30,0:17:54.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们来跟你讲讲真正的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:54.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll tell you the real story
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  什么故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what's the story?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.88,0:18:01.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村的工业巨头  泡芙先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:18:01.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Bikini Bottom's own titan of industry, Mr. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.18,0:18:04.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开发了第一条汽船流水线  大获成功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:04.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ran the first successful boat assembly line
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.52,0:18:12.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让工人尽可能高效工作非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:10.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was important for every worker
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to perform as efficiently as possible
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加快五号流水线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Speed up line number five
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.20,0:18:26.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正在加快五号流水线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:26.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Speeding up line number five
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.42,0:18:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工人有时会被工作缠得脱不开身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:39.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they'd get
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a little too caught up in their work
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.68,0:18:43.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:43.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.44,0:18:56.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是泡芙先生可精明了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:56.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But being a shrewd industrialist
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.61,0:18:59.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在隔壁也开了一家医院
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:59.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Puff also owned the hospital next door
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:18:59.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1298,622)}急诊
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哔哔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beep, beep
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now hold it just a darn minute
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:13.75,注释,,0,0,0,,[ screwball（荒诞） ]
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.09,0:19:17.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种荒诞故事不可能是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:17.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't no way these screwball stories are true
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.26,0:19:18.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看看牌子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:18.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me read that plaque
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工业巨头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Titan of industry"
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,流水线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Assembly line"
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.55,0:19:22.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:22.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Injuries"
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.47,0:19:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隔壁开医院
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Hospital next door"
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哔哔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Beep beep"?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, twist my tail
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.68,0:19:29.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:29.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all were right
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.81,0:19:30.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:30.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Told ya
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哔哔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beep beep
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.77,0:19:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村的历史果然多彩多姿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew Bikini Bottom's history would be colorful
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.82,0:19:40.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但答案太少  反而新问题又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:40.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'm starting to have more questions than answers
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许可以去顶楼的这个问号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe this question mark on the top floor
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.12,0:19:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就可以回答你所有问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is where you get your questions answered
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些忘记按了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You forgot to push these
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,迷幻海时代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Psychedelic Sea era
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:55.38,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 迷幻摇滚：摇滚乐流派\N深受嬉皮士文化影响 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.71,0:20:00.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,深海迪斯科时代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:00.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Deep Disco era
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.72,0:20:05.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新浪潮白痴时代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:05.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,New Wave Nitwits era
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:05.14,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 新浪潮：运用合成器和电子元素\N在MV中表现独特视觉风格 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四处探险时代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nautical Nonsense era
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.69,0:20:14.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这博物馆也太怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:14.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This sure is a weird museum
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.40,0:20:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里应该是幽灵展厅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess this is the ghost exhibit
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.32,0:20:24.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里应该还在施工  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think it's under construction, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.57,0:20:28.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等不及要看博物馆放幽灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:28.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait till they put the ghosts in
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a second
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.54,0:20:34.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道这是假牙佩戴器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:34.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this a denture applicator?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.29,0:20:38.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骨科喷气靴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:38.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Orthopedic jet boots
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.96,0:20:42.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原子成人尿布射线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:42.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The atomic adult diaper ray
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是成人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're adults
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:58.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,976)}未来裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.22,0:20:51.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:51.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.73,0:20:54.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不是一般的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:54.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This ain't no regular future, fellas
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.98,0:20:58.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是助步器老头统治的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:58.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is a future ruled by Old Man Walker
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:00.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1696,398)}安静
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:00.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(336,638)}滚出我草坪
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.15,0:21:05.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  小混混
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:05.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, you hooligans
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说了眼观手不动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:08.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said no touching
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.99,0:21:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.50,0:21:16.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们三个看到的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:16.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You three have seen too much
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我要来抓住你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now I'm going to get ya
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站好别动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay right there
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了  助步器老头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Old Man Walker
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不会泄露未来的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We won't tell nobody about the future
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.48,0:21:45.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听我说  我们看到了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:45.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody, we've seen the future
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.99,0:21:48.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但那是天机不可泄露
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:48.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's a secret
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.21,0:22:07.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,助步器老头必将把你们全统治了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:07.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Old Man Walker will rule you all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:12.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1004,466)}礼品店
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.76,0:22:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村的过去和未来就这样全看完了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, there goes Bikini Bottom's entire past and future
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.43,0:22:16.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  所以你说怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:16.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, Sandy, what'd you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.10,0:22:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还是将信将疑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm still skeptical
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村的过去太疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom's past was a bit too nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.77,0:22:23.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这松鼠可受不住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:23.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for this old squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.15,0:22:26.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过  起码裤头村现在挺正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:26.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But hey, at least Bikini Bottom is normal now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.99,0:22:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  基本算正常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, totally normal
